take letter
look up dispatch func in state
apply dispatch func to letter -> new turtle
look up current turtle in state
supply both turtles to side-effecting function
       in the case of size calculation:
          load current borders from state
          supply comparison func with borders, current turtle, new turtle
                 -> new borders, assoc'd into state
       in the case of drawing
          draw difference between turtles
               -> new turtle, assoc'd into state

